 {\"ngram\": \"a gruelling marathon\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"a first medal\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weir found one last ride down one of the most famous avenues in the world was a painful, not prideful, experience.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"one last ride\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"the most famous avenues\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"a painful, not prideful, experience\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not the best feeling because we have got no suspension on our chairs,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best feeling\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"no suspension\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"our chairs\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's brutal to be honest.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are some smooth bits where it's got a little bit of tarmac in between, but it's just hit and miss.\\\"\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some smooth bits\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"tarmac\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is as good a metaphor as you will ever find for Weir's entire career, spanning seven Paralympics.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as good a metaphor\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"Weir's entire career\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"seven Paralympics\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly selected for Barcelona 1992 as a 14-year-old, his first Paralympics could have been his last and he stepped away disillusioned by the sparse crowds at Atlanta 1996.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.337926893872245e-13, \"text\": \"Barcelona 1992\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1992_Summer_Paralympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1429, \"end\": 1441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.637621579174703e-12, \"text\": \"Atlanta 1996\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1996_Summer_Paralympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first Paralympics\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"the sparse crowds\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Revitalised by watching the success of Sydney at home on TV, Weir returned after a long time away to feature in Athens and win a crucial pair of medals over 100m and 200m.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999047177016, \"rank\": 9.481024400644426e-08, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 1556, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9726980791637035, \"rank\": 0.028068237471432795, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"a crucial pair\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"100m\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"2012 was the big one, but before that Athens was the proudest moment,\\\" said Weir, \\\"to come back from having two or three years out and get on that podium.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9726980791637035, \"rank\": 0.028068237471432795, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the proudest moment\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"that podium\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not think I'd ever do it and that gave me the stepping stone to want more and more.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stepping stone\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think if I did not win there, I probably would not be here now.\\\"\", \"from\": 1865, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weir became a household name with four golds at London 2012, cementing his legacy with the best possible performance at the best possible time.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1981, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\", \"score\": 0.999971938803267, \"rank\": 2.7581977979763012e-05, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Paralympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"a household name\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"four golds\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"his legacy\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible performance\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible time\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At least in terms of results at the Games, his performances have nosedived since then and Rio 2016 was a miserable experience as he felt \\\"stabbed in the back\\\" by his team.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"results\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"his performances\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"a miserable experience\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once again, Weir stepped away and announced his first retirement in 2017 but life in the shadows has never been for him and he was back a year later chasing Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9329613085473244, \"rank\": 0.07185581034864288, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"his first retirement\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"the shadows\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did not cut a happy figure three years ago either, railing against a lack of investment in his racing chair as he was overtaken by Swiss star Marcel Hug in a 'Ferrari of a chair'.\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_people\", \"score\": 0.8979724906116081, \"rank\": 0.11361982498150403, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2561, \"end\": 2571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Hug\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marcel Hug\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Hug\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Hug\"}, {\"begin\": 2578, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scuderia_Ferrari\", \"score\": 0.9999864827881989, \"rank\": 1.3517392820619585e-05, \"text\": \"Ferrari\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scuderia_Ferrari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scuderia_Ferrari\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a happy figure\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2445}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"his racing chair\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"a chair\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weir clocked his first 5000m personal best in 14 years earlier in 2024 to prove he is still a force, but the results were not forthcoming in Paris, finishing eighth in the 5000, going out in the heats of the 1500m and failing to figure at the sharp end of the marathon.\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2741, \"end\": 2746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.119257072775611e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2604}, {\"ngram\": \"his first 5000m\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2628}, {\"ngram\": \"a force\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the heats\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1500m\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2813}, {\"ngram\": \"the sharp end\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just think I have had a really tough week at my age,\\\" he reflected.\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really tough week\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"my age\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe I should have taken the decision just to do the marathon and I would have just come in yesterday and done it.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I got myself back up to the ranking list (in the 5km) and I have had a good year.\\\"\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ranking list\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3103}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5km\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"a good year\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weir told team officials that he would announce his retirement in the immediate aftermath of the Paris marathon despite wife Victoria pleading with him not to.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3244, \"end\": 3258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Marathon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris marathon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Marathon\"}, {\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoria_Australian_rules_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9996918785072111, \"rank\": 0.00030747787618089467, \"text\": \"Victoria\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoria_Australian_rules_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victoria_Australian_rules_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3151}, {\"ngram\": \"team officials\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"his retirement\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"the immediate aftermath\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud and very emotional,\\\" said Weir.\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To span a career since 1996, I have been at the top of my game for a long time.\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 3361, \"to\": 3369}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3404}, {\"ngram\": \"my game\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3415}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had bad years and good years, but that's just the way I have worked throughout my career.\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bad years\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3455}, {\"ngram\": \"good years\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3470}, {\"ngram\": \"just the way\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rio was probably my worst Games.\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"my worst Games\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have really enjoyed being here.\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team's been great.\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to thank the team, what they have done for me here, just looking after me and they have just been the best team ever.\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3648}, {\"ngram\": \"the best team\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Always, always, always proud to wear the flag.\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the flag\", \"from\": 3786, \"to\": 3794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's quite sad that I will not wear it again.\\\"\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Weir will continue to nurture the next generation of wheelchair racing talent through his Weir Archer Academy, with academy product Marcus Perrineau-Daley winning 100m silver on debut in Paris.\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 4037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3939, \"end\": 3945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archery\", \"score\": 0.9989887191923014, \"rank\": 0.0010123045317597245, \"text\": \"Archer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archery\"}, {\"begin\": 3976, \"end\": 3982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"score\": 0.9999999999076863, \"rank\": 9.223820174259549e-11, \"text\": \"Marcus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\